    "Following the same scenario, Pulkkinen et al. [222] proposed a model-based DRL algorithm for online waveform design.",
    "Specifically, the environment structural information was assumed to be available, which can boost the training efficiency of the DRL algorithm.",
    "They also observed that the model-free algorithm was superior to the model-based counterpart when the training data were sufficient.",
    "Qi et al. [223] also investigated the interference mitigation problem within ISAC networks.",
    "In particular, the ISAC-BS first transmitted the sensing waveform and then received the echo and uplink communication signal from the communication users."
